{
  "id": "S2P05K62",
  "title": {
    "product_var": "ZPRODTSK",
    "text": "CUSTOM KEY ASSIGNMENT",
    "version_var": "ZSHRTVER",
    "prefix": "HELP"
  },
  "type": "help",
  "body": {
    "rows": [
      {
        "type": "command",
        "variable": "ZCMD"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "At this point, hit the custom key to be defined.  For example,"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "if you hit the \"5\" key in the middle of the numeric keypad, the"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "KEY NAME display should change to something like:"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "KEY NAME:   CUSTOM-1234"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "However, if you hit a key that SPF/PC recognizes, then it will"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "display a label describing the key.  If you were to hit the"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "ENTER key on the numeric keypad, then it would change as follows:"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "KEY NAME:   Enter-Ext"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "If you hit a key that is defined already in one of the other"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "key assignment tables (like F6), or you hit a key that is not"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "assignable (like 'A'), SFP/PC will beep."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Once the KEY NAME represents the key you want to assign a value"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "to, hit the Enter key.  If you want to abort, exiting without"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "assigning a value to any new key, then hit F3."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "field_row",
        "fields": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "(Press"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "ENTER+to continue)"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
  "metadata": {
